values: So, when I get home from school, me and my dad get into a big arguement, and like always, he makes me feel like shit. what ever man. then andrew calls me, and asks me if i wanna go to the mall... so I say yes, and he picks me up, and fat joes with him. well.. little did I know this trip would end with andrew going to jail. haha. well we pull up and, he was talking about stealin, and i told him, no because i had a bad feeling. WELL.. he goes in, with fatjoe. fatjoe walks out 3 seconds later, because "they didnt have anything he wanted". well, me and joe sit in the car for like an hour, then we call andrew, no answer. we call him again and again, no answer. Joe goes in. can find him. he comes out, no andrew. he goes in like 10 mins later, can't find him. then as 2 hours roll around, ME and joe go in, cant find him, walk threw the WHOLE mall; no andrew. we go to the car again, hopeing hes there, ha no. well, we call adam, asking him if hes heard form andrew. he says no, and joe asks him if he has any way for us to get home, so adam says he'll call us back, he has his fiunred frank come get us, STILL not knowing where or what happened to andrew, well. after frink drops me off, i call adam to have him call me when he finds out, and he tells me andrews in jail WOW. lol I knew we had gotten caught. lol. well then i get home STILL in a good mood. i talk to someone, and he gets mad at me for no reason. "flustered" what does that mean anyways?

Soo, today I got home, and went down to Sarah's to see the puppy=] then, I hung out with Jeffy =] We did alot. ;] jk. No BUTT.. we went to Kmart for my sister to take bottles back, and we were flicking bottle caps at each other, then he smacked my butt REALLY hard, so i sack tapped him, lmao, and he fell on the ground. it was funny, then, we took my sister home and went to mickey d's and he was making weird ass noises when he was eating his cheese burger just to be gay, lmao, then he was trying to eat my ice cream, when he HAD a shake, lol. Then we got in the car, and he was driving like a crazy kid, and he made me spill my ice cream on myself, and he hit the breaks hard, and my water FLEW, and spilled EVERYWHERE. and he laughed at me =[. Then we stood in the middle of the street and played slaps for like a half hour. Our hands were REDDDDD, then he wanted my pants but I told him no, then he kept hitting my sun burn, and i was getting mad >:[ but he's cute && i had fun =]

So this weekend, I had a lot of fun.
Usually when i'm not home it keeps my mind off of things. Amanda's party was fun. Then I come home and everything just comes to me. Why my life/love lifes the way it is. And I think to myself maybe god intended for me to just wanna give up all the time. I mean theres really no other way to explain it right? Well idk, then I think of the quote. "I've givin up on love, because loves givin up on me." =/ I'm absolutly numb to the feeling of how everything has been going for me lately, it's absolutly re-god-damn-diculous.
UGH, sometimes I think i'm just wasting my time, but yeah, I hung out with Drew today, and we went and saw my nephew, he's SOOOOOOO cute [my nephew]. CHEA =]
Well, im pretty much not mad anymore, actully im in a good mood today =], and im in the kinda mood where, whatever happens; happens, ya know? HAH.
Well, i'm pretty much finding out all boys are the same, their not gonna change, BLAH.
